# Button Cursor Pointer

Always add `cursor-pointer` to interactive elements:

- `<button>` elements
- Elements styled as buttons (e.g. `role="button"` or clickable divs)
- Custom link-like elements that trigger actions on click

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
<button className="... cursor-pointer">Click me</button>
<a className="... cursor-pointer" onClick={...}>Action</a>

// ❌ BAD
<button className="...">Click me</button>
```
